{"data": [{"id": "4745704", "title": "Upstart Holdings: The Storm Has Passed", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Percentage Sign On Top Of Coin Stacks Before Blue Financial Graph\" data-id=\"1503371245\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MicroStockHub</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Well over two years ago, one company that I decided to take a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4509938-upstart-holdings-q1-earnings-buying-opportunity\">bullish stance</a> on was <b>Upstart Holdings, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UPST\" title=\"Upstart Holdings, Inc.\">UPST</a></span>). In case you aren't familiar with the business, it operates as a cloud-based AI lending</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1503371245/image_1503371245.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745704-upstart-holdings-the-storm-has-passed", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 01:33:49", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745701", "title": "TFI International - Monitor Before Pulling The Trigger", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"T-Force Freight linehaul semi-truck heading west on Interstate 90 from Spokane, Washington USA.\" data-id=\"2148550106\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jon Tetzlaff/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction &amp; Thesis</h2> <p>TFI International (NY: <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TFII\" title=\"TFI International Inc.\">TFII</a></span> &amp; TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TFII:CA\" class=\"ticker-link\">TFII:CA</a>) is a large North American logistics and transport company with a diversified portfolio of business spanning truckload (TL), less-than-truckload (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LTL\" title=\"ProShares Trust - ProShares Ultra Telecommunications\">LTL</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745701-tfi-international-monitor-before-pulling-the-trigger", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 01:28:57", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745699", "title": "Buy The Dip: High-Yield High-Growth Stocks Getting Way Too Cheap", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money Saving Graph\" data-id=\"2158301126\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Federal Reserve's announcement that they anticipate fewer rate cuts moving forward than previously projected in their dot plot has sent markets into a panic. This recent drop only accelerated the pullbacks already being experienced by several high-yield, high-growth stocks that appear</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745699-buy-the-dip-high-yield-high-growth-stocks-getting-way-too-cheap", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 01:14:40", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745697", "title": "URNJ: A Great Value Opportunity", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nuclear power station\" data-id=\"182860157\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jan-Otto/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Holdings</h2> <p>The Sprott Junior Uranium Miners ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/URNJ\" title=\"Sprott Junior Uranium Miners ETF\">URNJ</a></span>) is an ETF focused on small and mid-cap uranium miners. It has quite a bit of overlap with the Sprott Uranium Miners ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/URNM\" title=\"Exchange Traded Concepts Trust - North Shore Global Uranium Mining ETF\">URNM</a>), but URNJ doesn't own the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745697-urnj-a-great-value-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 01:10:19", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745693", "title": "Toro: The Stability Investors Need In The Next Tariff Cycle", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young woman controlling robot lawn mower in summer garden\" data-id=\"1279478271\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Finn Hafemann/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Toro Company (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TTC\" class=\"ticker-link\">TTC</a>) will be immune to tariffs as most of the products are manufactured in the U.S.A. The company is focusing on offering higher-margin products in its portfolio by consolidating brands and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745693-toro-the-stability-investors-need-in-the-next-tariff-cycle", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:57:54", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745691", "title": "FRI: Real Estate ETF With Some Exclusions And A High Fee", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Real estate growth graph\" data-id=\"2148675525\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1063px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Rasi Bhadramani</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>FRI strategy</strong></h2> <p><strong>First Trust S&amp;P REIT Index Fund</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FRI\" title=\"First Trust S&amp;P REIT Index Fund ETF\">FRI</a></span>) was launched on 5/8/2007 and tracks the S&amp;P United States REIT Index. It has a portfolio of 136 equity REITs, a 30-day SEC yield of 3.16% and a net</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745691-fri-real-estate-etf-with-some-exclusions-and-a-high-fee", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:54:16", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745689", "title": "Investing Amid Fed Uncertainty: Where To Place Your Bets Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Department of Treasury\" data-id=\"2163652419\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Douglas Rissing</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>U.S. stocks sold off Wednesday, were neutral on Thursday, and are up quite a bit on Friday as I'm submitting final edits. A lot of realized volatility despite the fed cutting once more by the consensus 0.25bp. However, the Federal Reserve is now</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745689-investing-amid-fed-uncertainty-where-to-place-your-bets-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:49:19", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745688", "title": "iHeartMedia: An Underpriced 'Call Option'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A home studio for recording podcasts\" data-id=\"1472176196\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/